\v 13 Davide zunu loungoi …†aaza…†ani  čolu, nii eŐĀ poluvaawogi woni ma, eŐĀ …†…õ ma: ¬ęMini nu …†a ga …óe?¬Ľ Naa goo…†aa čoteni, eŐĀ …†…õ ma: ¬ęK…õŐÄ…õ …†a ga Amal…õke zunui ta, nii paai seik…Ē…†…Ēmai ma zooi nii zu.¬Ľ
